description:
Help Matisse repair the rocket by collecting fishies!
Jump, fly and conquer the 3D unravelling world with beautiful music score and addictive gameplay. The world floating in space pops in and out of view, the flying fish give Mattise jet pack power!

Can you fix the rocket and return to Earth safely?
name: Matisse's 3D World
intro: Help Matisse repair the cat's rocket, fly, jump and collect the fishies to return to Earth!
